This project, Mini-Ngram viewer is minimal version of Google Bookâ€™s Ngram Viewer (https://books.google.com/ngrams/)

This project is built in Python + Django for web hosting.

For charting functionality, I have used - Graphos Charting Library (http://agiliq.com/demo/graphos/)

############################## SETUP ##############################################

The following steps are to setup the project -

1. Download the project, unzip it and place it a directory

2. cd /path/to/directory

3. Run 

pip install -r requirements.txt

This will install the required packages needed

4. Run

python manage.py runserver

5. Check the terminal to see if the server is running

6. Go to -

https://127.0.0.1:8000/ngram_viewer_app/

on your browser

############################## RESULT ##############################################

The project supports 5-grams, However, it takes 17 mins to process the corpus for 5 grams. 

4-gram - 12 mins
3-gram - 7 mins
2-gram - 3 mins
1-gram - less than a min

You can change the number of grams to process in constants.py file. The variable is NGRAMS. By default it is set to 3.

